<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>89</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A dai zan, A thiang zan, Zeizong vialte a dai, Nau le a nu velchum ah
 A dawhmi ceunak aa zel, Dai tein aa hngilh ko, Dai tein aa hngilh ko.

[V2]
 A dai zan, A thiang zan, Khuamui a ceu dih cang, Tuukhal nih van hla
 an theih Hallelujah! Siangpahrang, Kan Khamhtu a chuak cang, Kan Khamhtu
 a chuak cang.

[V3]
 A dai zan, A thiang zan, Khuaruahhar Arfi nih, Nichuah siangpahrang a
 hruai, Jesuh kha laksawng an pek, Khamhbawi Khrih a chuak cang, Jesuh
 Khrih a chuak cang.

[V4]
 A dai zan, Thiang bik zan, Van arfi, Kan ceuh tuah, Vanmi he
 Hallelujah! Siangpahrang thangthat u si, Khrih Khamhtu a chuak cang,
 Jesuh Khrih a chuak cang.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<title>A DAI ZAN, A THIANG ZAN CH89</title>
</song>